  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"article-body\" itemprop=\"articleBody\"\u003e        \u003cdiv\u003e\n        \u003ch3\u003eQuick Links\u003c/h3\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                                                                                    \u003cul\u003e\n                \u003cli\u003e\n                    \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                        \u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"#ai-content-detector---copyleaks\"\u003eAI Content Detector - Copyleaks\u003c/a\u003e\n                                        \u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n                                    \u003c/li\u003e\n            \u003c/ul\u003e\n                                                                                            \u003cul\u003e\n                \u003cli\u003e\n                    \n                                    \u003c/li\u003e\n            \u003c/ul\u003e\n                                                                                            \u003cul\u003e\n                \u003cli\u003e\n                    \n                                    \u003c/li\u003e\n            \u003c/ul\u003e\n            \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eAI content is the bane of our online existences; distinguishing between human and AI-generated text and images is becoming unfathomably difficult. That\u0026#39;s why I use these Chrome extensions to detect AI content quickly—they\u0026#39;ll become part of your daily browsing experience quicker than you think!\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"ai-content-detector---copyleaks\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan\u003e3 \u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cspan\u003e\n                            \u003ca href=\"https://chromewebstore.google.com/detail/AI%20Content%20Detector%20-%20Copyleaks/gplcmncpklkdjiccbknjjkoidpgkcakd\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eAI Content Detector - Copyleaks