son.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/open-source-image-generators-comparison.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/open-source-image-generators-comparison.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/open-source-image-generators-comparison.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/open-source-image-generators-comparison.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/open-source-image-generators-comparison.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/open-source-image-generators-comparison.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/open-source-image-generators-comparison.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"1680\" height=\"840\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"open source image generators comparison\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/open-source-image-generators-comparison.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/open-source-image-generators-comparison.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\n\n        \n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eI found BitMind\u0026#39;s analysis takes around 10 seconds per image, which can feel a bit slow when scrolling through image-heavy websites. During my testing, it correctly identified AI images roughly 70% to 80% of the time—not perfect, but certainly helpful as a first-pass detection tool.\u003c/p\u003e    \n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                            \n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/bitmind-chrome-extension-menu-with-word-counter-in-the-background.png\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/bitmind-chrome-extension-menu-with-word-counter-in-the-background.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/bitmind-chrome-extension-menu-with-word-counter-in-the-background.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/bitmind-chrome-extension-menu-with-word-counter-in-the-background.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/bitmind-chrome-extension-menu-with-word-counter-in-the-background.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/bitmind-chrome-extension-menu-with-word-counter-in-the-background.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/bitmind-chrome-extension-menu-with-word-counter-in-the-background.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/bitmind-chrome-extension-menu-with-word-counter-in-the-background.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/bitmind-chrome-extension-menu-with-word-counter-in-the-background.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"1334\" height=\"1000\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Bitmind Chrome extension menu with word counter in the background.\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/bitmind-chrome-extension-menu-with-word-counter-in-the-background.png\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/bitmind-chrome-extension-menu-with-word-counter-in-the-background.png\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eOne limitation you might face is that BitMind occasionally flags authentic photographs as AI-generated, as seen in the following image. This isn\u0026#39;t entirely the extension\u0026#39;s fault, as today\u0026#39;s AI images have become quite realistic, making the boundaries between real and synthetic increasingly blurry.\u003c/p\u003e    \n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                            \n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/a-real-photo-flagged-as-ai-generated-by-bitmind-chrome-extension.png\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/a-real-photo-flagged-as-ai-generated-by-bitmind-chrome-extension.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/a-real-photo-flagged-as-ai-generated-by-bitmind-chrome-extension.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/a-real-photo-flagged-as-ai-generated-by-bitmind-chrome-extension.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/a-real-photo-flagged-as-ai-generated-by-bitmind-chrome-extension.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/a-real-photo-flagged-as-ai-generated-by-bitmind-chrome-extension.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/a-real-photo-flagged-as-ai-generated-by-bitmind-chrome-extension.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/a-real-photo-flagged-as-ai-generated-by-bitmind-chrome-extension.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/a-real-photo-flagged-as-ai-generated-by-bitmind-chrome-extension.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"1274\" height=\"955\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"A real photo flagged as AI-generated by Bitmind Chrome extension.\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/a-real-photo-flagged-as-ai-generated-by-bitmind-chrome-extension.png\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/a-real-photo-flagged-as-ai-generated-by-bitmind-chrome-extension.png\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e While \u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/why-i-dont-trust-ai-photo-edits/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eI don\u0026#39;t trust AI to do most photo edits\u003c/a\u003e myself, having tools like BitMind helps spot potentially AI-generated content when verifying sources, fact-checking news, or simply satisfying your curiosity about whether that too-perfect image is actually real.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"hive-ai-detector\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan\u003e1 \u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cspan\u003e\n                            \u003ca href=\"https://chromewebstore.google.com/detail/hive-ai-detector/cmeikcgfecnhojcbfapbmpbjgllklcbi\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eHive AI Detector\u003c/a\u003e\n                    \u003c/span\u003e\n       \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe Hive AI Detector stands out for its versatility—it handles text, images, and even audio or video content, up to 30 seconds long. You can access it in multiple ways: highlight text and right-click to select Hive AI Detector from the menu, or use the draggable icon that opens a sidebar where you can paste content directly (up to 2,048 characters).\u003c/p\u003e    \n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                            \n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/hive-ai-chrome-extension-flagging-content-as-human-written-in-the-sidebar.png\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/hive-ai-chrome-extension-flagging-content-as-human-written-in-the-sidebar.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/hive-ai-chrome-extension-flagging-content-as-human-written-in-the-sidebar.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/hive-ai-chrome-extension-flagging-content-as-human-written-in-the-sidebar.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/hive-ai-chrome-extension-flagging-content-as-human-written-in-the-sidebar.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/hive-ai-chrome-extension-flagging-content-as-human-written-in-the-sidebar.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/hive-ai-chrome-extension-flagging-content-as-human-written-in-the-sidebar.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/hive-ai-chrome-extension-flagging-content-as-human-written-in-the-sidebar.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/hive-ai-chrome-extension-flagging-content-as-human-written-in-the-sidebar.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"1567\" height=\"1175\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Hive AI Chrome extension confirming content as human written in the sidebar.\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/hive-ai-chrome-extension-flagging-content-as-human-written-in-the-sidebar.png\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/hive-ai-chrome-extension-flagging-content-as-human-written-in-the-sidebar.png\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eFor images, right-click and select \u003cstrong\u003eHive AI Detector\u003c/strong\u003e from the context menu. Using this extension is handy because it not only tells you if an image is AI-generated but also tries to identify which specific AI model was likely used to create it, along with a confidence percentage.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                        \n    \n\n\u003cp\u003eWhile Hive\u0026#39;s accuracy seems solid, like \u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/accurate-ai-text-detectors/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eother AI detectors you can try\u003c/a\u003e, it sometimes delivers confusing results. This hit-or-miss nature is unfortunately common with detection tools, as \u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/how-ai-and-machine-learning-can-detect-and-prevent-malicious-attacks/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eAI can detect and prevent malicious attacks\u003c/a\u003e, but still struggles with perfect accuracy.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eThe best part? You don\u0026#39;t need to create an account or enter your email address to use this extension. Just install it and start using it. It respects your privacy while still providing a powerful detection tool.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eBut remember that these extensions are just tools to supplement your critical thinking. As AI content becomes more sophisticated, your gut feeling about authenticity might sometimes prove more reliable than any algorithm\u0026#39;s determination. Trust, but verify, that\u0026#39;s my approach to navigating the internet.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
